export const hasTop = (list) => {
  return (
    list.includes("Dish Dasha") ||
    list.includes("T-Shirt") ||
    list.includes("Girl T-Shirt") ||
    list.includes("Polo Shirt") ||
    list.includes("Shirt") ||
    list.includes("Long Shirt") ||
    list.includes("Jacket") ||
    list.includes("Girl Hoodie") ||
    list.includes("Suit") ||
    list.includes("Dress") ||
    list.includes("Tank Top") ||
    list.includes("Bra")
  );
};

export const hasBottom = (list) => {
  return (
    list.includes("Dish Dasha") ||
    list.includes("Pants") ||
    list.includes("Shorts") ||
    list.includes("Ragged Shorts") ||
    list.includes("Suit") ||
    list.includes("Dress") ||
    list.includes("Briefs")
  );
};

export const hasHeadWear = (list) => {
  return list.includes("Beanie") || list.includes("Snapback");
};

export const isVest = (list) => {
  return list.includes("Tank Top");
};

export const isFootWear = (list) => {
  return (
    list.includes("Vans") ||
    list.includes("Flip Flops") ||
    list.includes("Shoes") ||
    list.includes("Heels") ||
    list.includes("Socks")
  );
};
